{"tid":2342961,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"韓女團表演服印漢字遭內地網民狠批","createTime":"2020-12-27T13:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T14:03:14.000Z","uid":74392,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eaf5ee8a3ba8e98dfad16d9b87e1b7192bea58d4","tid":2342961,"uid":74392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20201227-17_VApeB_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20201227-17_VApeB_1200x0.png&h=a97f2020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼知名韓國男團防彈少年團（BTS）遭中國網民杯葛，韓國女團 MAMAMOO 早前表演的服裝亦惹來中國網民爭議，批評服飾「盜用」中國文化，包括衣服上印有「中文字」。服裝設計者 Leesle Hwang 反駁有關言論表示， MAMAMOO 當日穿著的是「現代韓服」，衣服上的文字是來自世宗大王於 1446 年頒布的《訓民正音》，反問「世宗大王是中國人嗎？」不理解為何韓國人穿韓國服飾存在問題。<br />\n<br />\n原文：<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/韓女團表演服印漢字遭內地網民狠批-設計師指源世宗大王-韓網民-世宗是中國人嗎\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E9%9F%93%E5%A5%B3%E5%9C%98%E8%A1%A8%E6%BC%94%E6%9C%8D%E5%8D%B0%E6%BC%A2%E5%AD%97%E9%81%AD%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%8B%A0%E6%89%B9-%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E5%B8%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%BA%90%E4%B8%96%E5%AE%97%E5%A4%A7%E7%8E%8B-%E9%9F%93%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E4%B8%96%E5%AE%97%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%97%8E&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWLTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=a00ac5b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E9%9F%93%E5%A5%B3%E5%9C%98%E8%A1%A8%E6%BC%94%E6%9C%8D%E5%8D%B0%E6%BC%A2%E5%AD%97%E9%81%AD%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%8B%A0%E6%89%B9-%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E5%B8%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%BA%90%E4%B8%96%E5%AE%97%E5%A4%A7%E7%8E%8B-%E9%9F%93%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E4%B8%96%E5%AE%97%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%97%8E&h=66b4ef60\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/韓女團表演服印漢字遭內地網民狠批-設計師指源世宗大王-韓網民-世宗是中國人嗎</a><br />\n<br />\n又一地玻璃碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/do